 filmik na ten temat.<\/li>\n<li><b>Targetowanie odbiorc\u00f3w<\/b>: Zauwa\u017c, \u017ce targetowanie odbiorc\u00f3w w reklamach Sponsored Display nie przynios\u0142o oczekiwanych efekt\u00f3w, dlatego nie jest to kluczowa strategia.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><b>Podsumowuj\u0105c<\/b>, skuteczne wykorzystanie reklam Sponsored Product na Amazonie wymaga precyzyjnego okre\u015blenia cel\u00f3w oraz bie\u017c\u0105cej optymalizacji kampanii. Zastosowanie powy\u017cszych wskaz\u00f3wek pomo\u017ce Ci zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 widoczno\u015b\u0107 Twoich produkt\u00f3w.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><b>Jak skutecznie wykorzysta\u0107 reklamy na Amazonie?<\/b> Je\u015bli chcesz, aby Twoje produkty w kategorii <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4822,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4821","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-strategia"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4821"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4821"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4821\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4822"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4821"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=